499
00:28:54.232 --> 00:28:55.692
[Indira] <i>Desiderio Island.</i>

500
00:28:55.775 --> 00:28:58.194
<i>Hmm. what else do you know</i>
<i>about this cult?</i>

501
00:28:58.903 --> 00:29:00.405
[Camila] <i>They're polyamorous.</i>

502
00:29:00.488 --> 00:29:02.157
[woman screaming]

503
00:29:02.240 --> 00:29:03.658
<i>They believe in freedom.</i>

504
00:29:04.617 --> 00:29:05.910
<i>in self-government.</i>

505
00:29:05.994 --> 00:29:08.246
<i>and that emotions are</i>
<i>the foundation of everything.</i>

506
00:29:10.790 --> 00:29:12.417
[baby crying]

507
00:29:14.043 --> 00:29:17.046
<i>I'm positive</i>
<i>that Eva is living among them.</i>

508
00:29:17.130 --> 00:29:20.133
[suspenseful music playing]

509
00:29:23.595 --> 00:29:26.806
Oh. yes. You're so beautiful.
You're perfect.

510
00:29:30.518 --> 00:29:33.605
He mentioned that he saw her
among the rest of the cult members.

511
00:29:33.688 --> 00:29:35.857
It's very hard
to get access to that island.

512
00:29:36.608 --> 00:29:37.650
Please. help.

513
00:29:37.734 --> 00:29:38.568
[music ends]

514
00:29:46.951 --> 00:29:47.911
Oliver.

515
00:29:49.746 --> 00:29:54.626
I don't know if you'll believe me at all…
but I wanted the best for both of us.

516
00:29:56.711 --> 00:29:58.171
I thought if I got out first.

517
00:29:58.254 --> 00:30:00.131
then I could free you
from that awful orphanage.

518
00:30:00.215 --> 00:30:01.132
but I was wrong.

519
00:30:02.383 --> 00:30:03.718
[intriguing music playing]

520
00:30:06.596 --> 00:30:08.389
INDENTIFICATION RECORD

521
00:30:08.473 --> 00:30:09.599
So I burned your papers.

522
00:30:12.101 --> 00:30:13.478
I did it to protect you.

523
00:30:13.561 --> 00:30:14.771
I needed to get out first

524
00:30:14.854 --> 00:30:18.024
because I believed
I could fix everything from the outside.

525
00:30:18.107 --> 00:30:18.983
make it all better.

526
00:30:19.567 --> 00:30:20.944
And then I asked about you.

527
00:30:22.403 --> 00:30:23.822
They told me you were doing great.

528
00:30:23.905 --> 00:30:25.740
that you had been adopted
by a family like mine.

529
00:30:25.824 --> 00:30:26.783
and I was so relieved.

530
00:30:26.866 --> 00:30:30.370
Because for me. it was better
to think that you were adopted

531
00:30:31.579 --> 00:30:33.456
than accept that I had abandoned you.

532
00:30:34.165 --> 00:30:36.376
You didn't give a shit about me
at all. bastard!

533
00:30:36.459 --> 00:30:37.293
Not true.

534
00:30:37.377 --> 00:30:40.255
You didn't care about my fucking life.
you son of a bitch.

535
00:30:40.338 --> 00:30:42.257
And why? Tell me. motherfucker!

536
00:30:42.340 --> 00:30:44.342
- Hey! I already told you!
- You asshole!

537
00:30:44.425 --> 00:30:46.636
I was wrong. man! I failed. okay?!

538
00:30:46.719 --> 00:30:49.389
And now I'm begging for forgiveness.

539
00:30:49.472 --> 00:30:50.765
[breathing shakily]

540
00:30:53.351 --> 00:30:55.436
Listen. I'm so sorry. okay? I said it.

541
00:30:56.855 --> 00:30:59.732
[breath trembling] You son of a bitch.

542
00:31:00.525 --> 00:31:02.318
[Oliver panting]

543
00:31:11.536 --> 00:31:13.705
[Indira] Okay.
there is something strange here.

544
00:31:13.788 --> 00:31:14.831
[phone ringing]

545
00:31:17.500 --> 00:31:19.586
Where have we seen this image before?

546
00:31:22.380 --> 00:31:23.715
In Duval's case file.

547
00:31:24.340 --> 00:31:28.720
These photos were discovered
in his cell after his suicide.

548
00:31:35.351 --> 00:31:36.311
[Indira exhales]

549
00:31:39.689 --> 00:31:41.190
Camila was right on this.

550
00:31:41.691 --> 00:31:45.445
- This could be any island though.
- [Indira] No. It's Desiderio Island.

551
00:31:45.528 --> 00:31:47.196
Here. It's where we'll find Eva.

552
00:31:47.906 --> 00:31:48.865
[exhales]

553
00:31:49.449 --> 00:31:50.366
Duval.

554
00:31:51.409 --> 00:31:53.745
[dramatic sting]

555
00:31:53.828 --> 00:31:57.498
After the kidnapping.
Camila was never the same again.

556
00:31:57.999 --> 00:32:00.209
Finding that girl became
an obsession to her.

557
00:32:00.293 --> 00:32:03.254
She wouldn't stop. and she was blinded
to the dangers around her.

558
00:32:03.338 --> 00:32:04.213
and I warned her.

559
00:32:04.297 --> 00:32:07.300
I told her
she was taking unnecessary risks.

560
00:32:07.383 --> 00:32:10.887
[sighs] Indira. you did
everything you could for that woman.

561
00:32:10.970 --> 00:32:11.846
Everything.

562
00:32:12.513 --> 00:32:15.642
I knew she felt guilty
when she brought Eva to that party

563
00:32:15.725 --> 00:32:19.145
and even more so
for not getting her parents' permission.

564
00:32:19.228 --> 00:32:21.272
and for causing Miguel pain.

565
00:32:21.356 --> 00:32:22.482
I feel for her.

566
00:32:22.982 --> 00:32:23.816
Making it worse.

567
00:32:23.900 --> 00:32:27.195
the man she trusted most at that time.
her ex-husband David.

568
00:32:27.278 --> 00:32:29.864
turned out to be an accomplice to Ángela.

569
00:32:30.490 --> 00:32:34.577
That man completely betrayed her trust
and assisted you in the investigation.

570
00:32:34.661 --> 00:32:35.495
[Indira] True.

571
00:32:35.578 --> 00:32:38.122
And if it hadn't been for David.
we'd have no evidence

572
00:32:38.206 --> 00:32:41.209
that Eva would be living with that cult
on the island.

573
00:32:41.793 --> 00:32:44.212
David Meneses. Joaquín Duval.

574
00:32:45.672 --> 00:32:47.507
Ángela Ferrer. and all her followers

575
00:32:47.590 --> 00:32:50.343
will wind up paying
for every crime they have committed.

576
00:32:51.469 --> 00:32:55.723
Yep. even though he's cooperating.
they'll still prosecute David.

577
00:32:55.807 --> 00:32:57.892
but with Ángela Ferrer. you never know.

578
00:32:57.976 --> 00:33:00.478
She has avoided prosecution already.

579
00:33:00.561 --> 00:33:02.855
and if we don't prove she's involved

580
00:33:02.939 --> 00:33:06.526
as a murder accomplice
in the case of Santiago del Río

581
00:33:06.609 --> 00:33:08.319
and that she's involved
in the kidnapping of…

582
00:33:08.403 --> 00:33:09.779
Just think about it. boss.

583
00:33:11.155 --> 00:33:14.033
She shows up on the news
devastated and emotional.

584
00:33:14.117 --> 00:33:18.204
yet she was actually the one who planned
the kidnapping of her own daughter

585
00:33:18.287 --> 00:33:20.248
just to get back at Camila.

586
00:33:20.915 --> 00:33:23.334
Ángela knew about the island all along.

587
00:33:24.502 --> 00:33:25.586
[exhales] Crazy.

588
00:33:26.087 --> 00:33:29.757
And that guy who was her main accomplice
then betrayed her completely.

589
00:33:29.841 --> 00:33:33.511
Yes. that's because her main accomplice is
just as crazy as she is.

590
00:33:33.594 --> 00:33:36.222
I don't believe
a happy ending is a likely outcome here.

591
00:33:36.305 --> 00:33:38.182
We've already lost too many lives.

592
00:33:38.683 --> 00:33:41.561
I'm not optimistic
about how all of this is gonna go down.

593
00:33:41.644 --> 00:33:42.603
TWO DEAD IN A CULT

594
00:33:42.687 --> 00:33:45.898
There's no way
that this ends well for anyone.

595
00:33:46.941 --> 00:33:47.775
Yeah.

596
00:33:49.402 --> 00:33:51.195
[intriguing music playing]

597
00:34:04.792 --> 00:34:07.503
[Indira over radio] <i>Camila.</i>
<i>what's your status? Please respond.</i>

598
00:34:07.587 --> 00:34:09.547
[Camila] <i>I'm on my way to the island.</i>

599
00:34:09.630 --> 00:34:13.301
- [Indira] <i>Everything okay so far?</i>
<i>- Yes. I haven't been recognized.</i>

600
00:34:13.384 --> 00:34:15.720
[Indira] <i>Copy that.</i>
<i>We are tracking your location.</i>

601
00:34:19.682 --> 00:34:24.187
[man] <i>Welcome to Desiderio Island.</i>
<i>Please follow our sisters in green.</i>

602
00:34:24.270 --> 00:34:25.772
[inaudible]

603
00:34:31.152 --> 00:34:32.945
[Camila] <i>I can confirm</i>
<i>Eva is on the island.</i>

604
00:34:33.029 --> 00:34:35.156
<i>Repeat. confirming Eva is here.</i>
<i>I just saw her.</i>

605
00:34:35.239 --> 00:34:36.824
[Indira] <i>Copy that. Be safe.</i>

606
00:34:51.005 --> 00:34:52.840
Camila Román is on the island.

607
00:34:54.133 --> 00:34:55.468
[Joaquín] Are you sure about that?

608
00:34:56.010 --> 00:34:56.844
Yes. it's her.

609
00:34:56.928 --> 00:34:58.930
[suspenseful music playing]

610
00:35:12.568 --> 00:35:14.445
[Camila] <i>Fuck. they've recognized me.</i>

611
00:35:14.529 --> 00:35:18.574
[Indira] <i>Wait. who? Who recognized you?</i>
<i>Camila. answer me. What's happening?</i>

612
00:35:19.992 --> 00:35:21.452
<i>Camila. do you copy?</i>

613
00:35:26.040 --> 00:35:27.416
<i>Camila. are you there?</i>

614
00:35:27.959 --> 00:35:29.544
Outta the way. move!

615
00:35:29.627 --> 00:35:31.212
[Indira] <i>Send more units now!</i>

616
00:35:31.295 --> 00:35:33.381
Stop right there! Stop her! Watch out!

617
00:35:35.925 --> 00:35:37.343
Hey! Hey. stop!

618
00:35:39.720 --> 00:35:41.347
[Camila screams]

619
00:35:41.973 --> 00:35:44.267
[Camila panting]

620
00:35:45.184 --> 00:35:47.061
[Camila grunting]

621
00:35:47.145 --> 00:35:48.604
Let go of me! That's enough!

622
00:35:49.105 --> 00:35:50.398
[Indira] We've lost contact.

623
00:35:50.481 --> 00:35:53.151
She's not responding.
and we don't have her location.

624
00:35:54.152 --> 00:35:55.486
Until we find her.

625
00:35:56.445 --> 00:35:57.989
she's out there on her own.

626
00:35:59.740 --> 00:36:01.284
[Camila panting]

627
00:36:02.660 --> 00:36:04.453
No. no. [yelps]

628
00:36:04.996 --> 00:36:05.913
Let go of me!

629
00:36:06.789 --> 00:36:09.667
Shh. shh. shh. shh. Hold still.

630
00:36:10.751 --> 00:36:12.336
Shh.

631
00:36:12.420 --> 00:36:13.504
- Okay. here.
- [Camila grunts]

632
00:36:13.588 --> 00:36:15.298
[Camila panting]

633
00:36:15.381 --> 00:36:16.549
Right there.

634
00:36:16.632 --> 00:36:18.259
Hold still.

635
00:36:18.342 --> 00:36:19.677
You don't want to fall.

636
00:36:19.760 --> 00:36:21.137
[Camila panting]

637
00:36:21.220 --> 00:36:22.847
[tense music playing]

638
00:36:27.476 --> 00:36:28.895
Is everything prepared?

639
00:36:28.978 --> 00:36:30.229
Come on. let's get ready.

640
00:36:31.480 --> 00:36:33.024
Our guests will be here soon.

641
00:36:35.443 --> 00:36:36.986
[panting]

642
00:36:39.488 --> 00:36:40.907
Why did you kidnap Eva?

643
00:36:40.990 --> 00:36:44.535
Eva no longer exists.
Her new name is Adyanta. and I'm Bautista.

644
00:36:45.119 --> 00:36:46.037
[engine revving]

645
00:36:50.541 --> 00:36:52.376
You know what happens now. Camila?

646
00:36:53.836 --> 00:36:55.379
It's your turn to die.

647
00:36:56.631 --> 00:36:58.049
You bastard. stop!

648
00:36:58.132 --> 00:36:59.926
If you let her drop.
I swear I'll kill you!

649
00:37:00.009 --> 00:37:01.594
You think you're a real hero. Juan David?

650
00:37:01.677 --> 00:37:04.347
One more step and I let her fall.
so drop your gun.

651
00:37:05.097 --> 00:37:06.057
[Camila] David.

652
00:37:06.891 --> 00:37:07.767
[Joaquín] Tell her.

653
00:37:09.101 --> 00:37:12.355
Tell her what you're doing here.
She needs to hear it directly from you.

654
00:37:12.939 --> 00:37:14.232
Come on. tell her!

655
00:37:15.942 --> 00:37:18.569
A mother would do anything
for her family. Camila.

656
00:37:18.653 --> 00:37:21.530
You shouldn't have interfered.
You meddled with the plan.

657
00:37:22.615 --> 00:37:24.325
This was all Ángela's idea.

658
00:37:25.368 --> 00:37:27.119
She organized the kidnapping. all of it.

659
00:37:27.203 --> 00:37:30.289
When are you going to realize
that this woman has it in for you?

660
00:37:30.373 --> 00:37:32.708
- She's dead if you don't drop that gun!
- Okay. I will!

661
00:37:32.792 --> 00:37:35.336
It's down. okay?
All good. It's fine. Let's just chill.

662
00:37:36.045 --> 00:37:37.255
I'm sorry. okay?

663
00:37:39.423 --> 00:37:41.008
I didn't know what else to do.

664
00:37:41.092 --> 00:37:42.093
I'm sorry.

665
00:37:44.220 --> 00:37:45.096
[Miguel grunting]

666
00:37:45.805 --> 00:37:46.973
[Camila] David. help me!

667
00:37:47.473 --> 00:37:49.684
- Don't move! Don't move!
- [Miguel] Where's my daughter?!

668
00:37:50.393 --> 00:37:52.019
- Where is she?
- Take it easy.

669
00:37:52.103 --> 00:37:54.146
- Where is my daughter?!
- [Ángela] Where is Eva?

670
00:37:54.230 --> 00:37:55.231
Everyone chill out!

671
00:37:55.314 --> 00:37:57.900
Why the fuck are you asking that?
You're the one who kidnapped her!

672
00:37:57.984 --> 00:38:00.444
What are you talking about?
I haven't heard from her in a year!

673
00:38:00.528 --> 00:38:02.571
- Where is she?!
- No. wait.

674
00:38:02.655 --> 00:38:04.156
- What've you done with her?!
- Kill her!

675
00:38:04.240 --> 00:38:07.201
Ah. you idiots!
What's wrong with you? Don't touch me!

676
00:38:08.160 --> 00:38:09.704
[Miguel] Tell me the truth right now.

677
00:38:10.579 --> 00:38:12.373
So now you care about your family?

678
00:38:12.456 --> 00:38:15.626
You let me go or I'll drop her.
I swear to God.

679
00:38:16.252 --> 00:38:18.546
You know what? You should be rotting.

680
00:38:18.629 --> 00:38:21.799
Just like your horrible father.
you fucking psychopath!

681
00:38:23.718 --> 00:38:25.261
[Camila screams]

682
00:38:28.723 --> 00:38:32.268
[Miguel] No! Oh my God!
No! Camila! Camila!

683
00:38:32.351 --> 00:38:33.561
[grunting]

684
00:38:37.273 --> 00:38:38.858
[somber music playing]

685
00:38:41.861 --> 00:38:42.820
No!

686
00:38:43.821 --> 00:38:45.406
- No!
- [Ángela] No. honey.

687
00:38:45.489 --> 00:38:47.199
- [Eva wailing]
- Camila!

688
00:38:47.283 --> 00:38:50.494
[somber music continues]

689
00:39:12.767 --> 00:39:14.185
[music fades]

690
00:39:16.645 --> 00:39:20.483
["Under Your Spell"
by Moa L. Muñoz and Ryan T. Short playing]

691
00:39:23.778 --> 00:39:25.905
<i>♪ Black magic ♪</i>

692
00:39:25.988 --> 00:39:27.990
<i>♪ Ecstatic ♪</i>

693
00:39:28.074 --> 00:39:31.702
<i>♪ Can't help when I look at you ♪</i>

694
00:39:32.411 --> 00:39:34.580
<i>♪ Dramatic ♪</i>

695
00:39:34.663 --> 00:39:36.791
<i>♪ I panic ♪</i>

696
00:39:36.874 --> 00:39:40.294
<i>♪ One look. what am I to do? ♪</i>

697
00:39:58.104 --> 00:40:00.940
<i>♪ Losing control ♪</i>

698
00:40:02.316 --> 00:40:07.071
<i>♪ Can't let it go. go. go. go. go. go ♪</i>

699
00:40:09.240 --> 00:40:13.452
<i>♪ Is this heaven or is this hell? ♪</i>

700
00:40:13.953 --> 00:40:19.875
<i>♪ Can't talk 'cause I'm under your</i>
<i>Under your spell ♪</i>

701
00:40:20.543 --> 00:40:25.381
<i>♪ Yeah. I'm under your spell ♪</i>

702
00:40:26.340 --> 00:40:30.886
<i>♪ Is this heaven or is this hell? ♪</i>

703
00:40:31.387 --> 00:40:37.560
<i>♪ Can't talk 'cause I'm under your</i>
<i>Under your spell ♪</i>

704
00:40:38.269 --> 00:40:42.857
<i>♪ Yeah. I'm under your spell ♪</i>

705
00:40:45.317 --> 00:40:46.402
[music ends]

706
00:40:47.820 --> 00:40:49.363
[dramatic music playing]

707
00:40:55.119 --> 00:40:56.328
[music ends]
